title: Google reports strong Q3 profit says its rethinking everything about machine learning
text:
Google reports strong Q3 profit, says it's 'rethinking everything' about machine learning 
Computerworld Friday 23rd October, 2015 
It's already sorting your email and translating your voice searches, and machine learning will play a bigger role in Google's services moving forward....
